{"tid":2248141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(台灣最美的風景)小兄妹省錢只點鴨肉飯 “大哥哥”偷幫埋單","createTime":"2020-10-18T11:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T11:36:12.000Z","uid":75196,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b8c00abfe48c0c67297b5cf1d906bcdbc2b967","tid":2248141,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"彰化15歲，念高一的哥哥，帶著國小的妹妹去吃鴨肉飯，兄妹知道家中經濟狀況不好，只點了兩碗鴨肉飯，一名同時間去用餐的年輕男子，默默幫忙結帳，還交代有加點也算他的，店家準備打烊，也加菜送了小菜跟兩碗湯，兄妹吃得好飽，媽媽得知之後，社群PO文，尋找暖男大哥哥。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.tvbs.com.tw/amp/life/1402222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Famp%2Flife%2F1402222&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=4e0c6219\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.tvbs.com.tw/amp/life/1402222</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/36ccyNuqpHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F36ccyNuqpHU&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=ee8b0717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/36ccyNuqpHU</a>"},{"pid":"e6ab936a7fe31b8d9d955a0a2590836a277a73b1","tid":2248141,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"暖男<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ba729dbc28a75b9970654bd8f237d0f212219a","tid":2248141,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:27:08.000Z","msg":"係愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a06df5fcbee51d5edd601649f4a575c89233b7","tid":2248141,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"諗起一碗陽春麵"},{"pid":"edc840a4d257e72c333ae0e29744802f58291790","tid":2248141,"uid":294121,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"食咩鴨肉飯<br />\n食大哥哥條腸仔夠啦"},{"pid"